      <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><a name="system"></a><strong><font size="5">System 
        Requirements</font></strong><br>
        <a href="#top"><font size="1">back to top</font></a></font></p>
      <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">PCs must have the following 
        features to properly run Karaoke Monster:</font></p>
      <ol>
        <li><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">A high-speed broadband connection 
          to the Internet (&quot;hiccups&quot; in the connection speed will cause 
          synchronization problems)</font></li>
        <li><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> The latest version of the 
          Mozilla or Netscape web browser.</font></li>
        <li><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">A Java client (Netscape default install is sufficient)</font></li>
        <li><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Windows 2000 or later versions.</font></li>
      </ol>
      </td>
  </tr>
